thread.title: Lynne Donnelly
thread.title_full: Omega Rental Cars reviewed by Lynne Donnelly

author: Lynne Donnelly
title: Lynne Donnelly
text: Omega were easy to deal with, only my second time of hiring a car, so a little unsure. The staff were great, picked us up from the airport, took us to their facility where the car was ready for us, we were quickly on our way. Dropping it back was just as easy & they even took us to meet our ship. Thankyou to all the staff at Omega Auckland & Wellington.
